<title> color.js</title> color.js
<para>Displays a color picker.</para>
<bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h2"> Objects</bridgehead>
<bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h3"> OAT.Color()</bridgehead>
<para>Instantiates <computeroutput>OAT.Color</computeroutput> object.</para>
<bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h2"> Methods</bridgehead>
<bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h3"> OAT.Color::pick(x, y, callback)</bridgehead>
<para>Shows the picker at <computeroutput>[x, y]</computeroutput>.
 When user picks a color, <computeroutput>callback(color)</computeroutput> function is called.
 Color format is <computeroutput>#rgb</computeroutput>.</para>
